➜iQOO Z1 航海王定制版图赏，带着热血驶向伟大航路
https://www.ifanr.com/1354306?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=	23578
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354307" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05736-01_meitu_5.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="675" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05736-01_meitu_5.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05736-01_meitu_5-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05736-01_meitu_5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05736-01_meitu_5-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>1997 年 7 月 22 日，尾田荣一郎先生的《航海王》开始在集英社《周刊少年 Jump》连载。</p>
<p>在此后的 20 年，该系列漫画「俘虏」了无数少男少女的心。「我是要成为航海王的人」这句略显「中二」的话，相信在座各位都曾说过，或者听别人说过。</p>
<p>20 年后，iQOO 牵手《航海王》，打造了 iQOO Z1 航海王限量版。7 月 22 日上午 10 点，这款满载热血与情怀的手机，刚上架就「秒售罄」。</p>
<p>如果让你用一种颜色去描述记忆中的《航海王》，那路飞草帽的橘黄色，可能是最容易从脑海中被唤醒的。</p>
<p>在 iQOO Z1 航海王限量版的礼盒正面，路飞手扶橘黄色草帽，熟悉的画面一下子把我拉进了童年的回忆中。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354323" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05728-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05728-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05728-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05728-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05728-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>在路飞的右侧，用草帽同款颜色印制了 iQOO。很显然，iQOO Z1 航海王限量版的主色调便是这个充满活力的颜色。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354322" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05729-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05729-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05729-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05729-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05729-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>在礼盒侧面，我们也能看到 iQOO 与《航海王》的 Logo。不过这里《航海王》的 Logo 使用了白色的版本，更显质感。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354329" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05732-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05732-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05732-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05732-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05732-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>打开礼盒，大片的橘黄色映入眼帘。礼盒内从左到右分别为定制耳机、手机、定制雨伞三个区域。iQOO 在包装的印刷上，下了一些功夫。浮雕印刷工艺让设计细节得到较好的呈现。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354320" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05734-02.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05734-02.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05734-02-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05734-02-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05734-02-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>接着是手机包装盒，套壳与包装盒之间的阻尼感偏紧，需要力气大一些才能将包装盒推出。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354310" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05738-01.jpeg" alt="" width="5895" height="3930" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05738-01.jpeg 5895w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05738-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05738-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05738-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5895px) 100vw, 5895px" /></p>
<p>手机包装盒的配色与礼盒相同，都是黑色配橘黄。包装盒上的花纹有点像赛车上的碳纤维，暗示这台手机的性能在游戏上表现不俗。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354321" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05741-01.jpeg" alt="" width="5613" height="3742" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05741-01.jpeg 5613w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05741-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05741-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05741-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5613px) 100vw, 5613px" /></p>
<p>默认的手机屏保壁纸是《航海王》的角色集锦图，这也是这款手机的专属壁纸。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354311" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05747-01-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05747-01-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05747-01-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05747-01-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05747-01-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>机身背面是橘黄色配暗红色。背部 LOGO 中，有一颗很大的骷髅头标识，代表「出海前行的信念不可磨灭」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354318" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05749-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05749-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05749-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05749-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05749-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>手机摄像头共有三颗，分别是 4800 万物理像素主摄 + 112° 超广角摄像头 + 微距镜头。在摄像头边上还烙印着「ONE PIECE」，瞄准海盗们的宝藏，起航吧！</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354319" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05750-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05750-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05750-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05750-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05750-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>细看 iQOO 的 Logo，可以看到上面有精致的纹理。这一纹理取自《航海王》中的恶魔果实，并化作船绳牵系住骷髅船帆，「拥有异能的我们是要成为航海王的人」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354317" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05756-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05756-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05756-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05756-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05756-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>解锁手机后，航海王深度定制 UI 一览无余。6.57 英寸 144Hz 的竞速屏，分辨率为 2408*1080，最高亮度可达 400nit。视觉上看起来精致且流畅。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354331" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05757-01_meitu_2.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1066" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05757-01_meitu_2.jpg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05757-01_meitu_2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05757-01_meitu_2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05757-01_meitu_2-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>在壁纸库里，还有一套草帽一伙单人壁纸，可以 Pick 你最喜欢的草帽一伙成员。据 iQOO 官方介绍。这款航海王限量版手机设计过程耗时 4000 多个小时，前后推翻 50 多套方案，历经 15 道工序，才最终打磨出成品。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354332" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05760-01_meitu_3.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1066" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05760-01_meitu_3.jpg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05760-01_meitu_3-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05760-01_meitu_3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05760-01_meitu_3-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>机身右侧是支持指纹解锁的电源键和音量加减键。电源键使用了黄铜色的涂层，与机身背部的颜色呼应。指纹解锁的加入，也让我们在疫情防控常态化的今天，不必再苦恼戴口罩时无法人脸解锁。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354309" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05788-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05788-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05788-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05788-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05788-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>机身左侧是 SIM 卡卡槽。该机配备了联发科在今年全面冲击 5G 市场的旗舰处理器——天玑 1000Plus ，支持 5G + 5G 双卡双待，8GB + 256GB 版本售价 2499 元，性价比较高，可以作为年轻人的第一台 5G 手机。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354308" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05795-01-01.jpeg" alt="" width="5921" height="3947" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05795-01-01.jpeg 5921w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05795-01-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05795-01-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05795-01-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5921px) 100vw, 5921px" /></p>
<p>底部则是 type-C 充电口、扬声器和 3.5mm 耳机孔。手机附赠一块 44W 的「闪充头」，实测 30 分钟可将手机电量从 10% 充到 75%。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354336" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05801-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05801-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05801-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05801-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05801-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>该机内置了一块 4500mAh 大容量电池手机，实测重量 197.5 克，机身尺寸分别为 163.9 × 75.5 × 8.9（毫米），握持感方面营造的还不错。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354324" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05784-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05784-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05784-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05784-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05784-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>随手机附赠的，还有航海王定制耳机。包装盒上印着熟悉的「万里阳光号」（Thousand Sunny）狮子头标志。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354316" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05761-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05761-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05761-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05761-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05761-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>耳机的配色同样是黑+黄。橘黄色的耳机线看起来很阳光。盒内附赠了三组大小不同的耳帽，可以自由选择使用。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354315" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05762-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05762-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05762-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05762-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05762-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>耳塞侧面也印着「万里阳光号」的狮子头标志，非常可爱。该耳机长度为 1.3 米，带有麦克风线控，支持高清通话。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354325" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05763-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05763-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05763-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05763-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05763-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>用航海王定制手机和耳机，听着航海王主题曲，航海迷的专属仪式感一下子就出来了。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354333" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05765-01_meitu_4.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1066" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05765-01_meitu_4.jpg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05765-01_meitu_4-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05765-01_meitu_4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05765-01_meitu_4-1024x682.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>礼盒内还有一把航海王定制雨伞。伞套上印着 iQOO 和航海王的 Logo。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354314" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05766-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05766-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05766-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05766-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05766-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>雨伞体积很小，重量上也比较轻巧，放在包里不会有负担。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354313" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05768-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05768-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05768-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05768-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05768-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>将雨伞打开，内面是蓝黄相间的航海图，心情也会随着明亮的色彩而轻松起来。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354327" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05771-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05771-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05771-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05771-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05771-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>雨伞外部的一侧印着路飞肖像，造型与定制礼盒正面一致。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354326" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05774-01.jpeg" alt="" width="5693" height="3796" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05774-01.jpeg 5693w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05774-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05774-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05774-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 5693px) 100vw, 5693px" /></p>
<p>另一侧是 iQOO 和航海王的 Logo。伞的体积虽然小，但是撑起来之后，覆盖面积还可以，足够一人使用。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1354312" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05778-01.jpeg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05778-01.jpeg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05778-01-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05778-01-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/DSC05778-01-1024x683.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>在使用这部手机两天后，我最大的感受就是「童年好像回来了」。无处不在的航海王元素，都让我想起儿时「驶向伟大航路」的梦想。</p>
<p>不过随着岁月的「摧残」，我逐渐忘记儿时曾信誓旦旦寻找人生中「ONE PIECE」的目标。而现在，我想是时候重拾起这一信念了。</p>
